data.text:
A Special Storytime with the Nats Reading Ambassador!

Join the Library and the Washington Nationals for a special Summer Reading storytime. Listen to Sean Doolittle read a story. Following the storytime, Sean Doolittle will be available for autographs. Limit one signed item per person, and for children only. The Summer Reading Program is for all ages and anyone who completes the challenge wins a voucher for free tickets to a Washington Nationals baseball game. So join us in celebrating Summer Reading and the Washington Nationals! Go Nats!

Registration not required.

For more information, contact LibraryPrograms@arlingtonva.us
